library(networkD3)
 
org_info <- read.csv("org_list.csv", stringsAsFactors = F)


aff_edgelist <- read.csv("ElectedOfficialsEdgesWAffiliationAndBounds.csv", 
                         stringsAsFactors = F)

aff_edgelist <- aff_edgelist %>% select(source = source_affil, target = target_afil) %>%
    filter(source != "")

colnames(org_info)[1] <- "source"
colnames(org_info)[2] <- "source_org"
aff_edgelist <- inner_join(aff_edgelist, org_info, by = "source")

colnames(org_info)[1] <- "target"
colnames(org_info)[2] <- "target_org"
aff_edgelist <- inner_join(aff_edgelist, org_info, by = "target")

level_edgelist <- aff_edgelist %>% group_by(source_org, target_org) %>% mutate(out_degree = length(target_org)) %>%
  group_by(source_org, target_org) %>% filter(row_number(out_degree) == 1)
g <- graph.data.frame(level_edgelist %>% select(source_org, target_org))
E(g)$size <- level_edgelist$out_degree
V(g)$color <- c("green", "green", "red", "red", "red")

plot(g, edge.width = E(g)$size / 5,
     edge.arrow.size=E(g)$size / 100,
     vertex.color = V(g)$color)

org_edgelist <- aff_edgelist %>% group_by(source, target) %>% 
  mutate(out_degree = length(target)) %>%
  group_by(source, target) %>% filter(row_number(out_degree) == 1)
g <- graph.data.frame(org_edgelist %>% select(source, target))
E(g)$size <- org_edgelist$out_degree
V(g)$label.cex = .75

plot(simplify(g), edge.width = E(g)$size,
     edge.arrow.size=E(g)$size / 10)

simpleNetwork(org_edgelist %>% select(source, target),
              zoom= TRUE)

org_edgelist %>% select(source, target) %>% group_by(source) %>% 
  mutate(out_degree = length(source)) %>% ungroup() %>% select(source, out_degree) %>%
  group_by(source) %>% filter(row_number(out_degree) == 1)
